AddressInfo.Title: EV Expert Administrative Building Courtyard
AddressInfo.AccessComments:
Charging station is in the courtyard. There is reception 24 / 7 and they grant you entrance to the courtyard (+420 603 202 676). 

If required, show this text to the reception staff:
"Prosím pusťte tohoto hosta s autem do dvora. Jede nabíjet na stanici EV Expert ve dvoře. S panem Jonášem je to domluvené. Děkuji."

GeneralComments: You can pay directly from our Web application, we use secure international online payment gate Barion. You must choose tariff, which is basically a reservation amount. The more you reserve, the cheaper is kWh. The money that you will not spend will be reimbursed to your account in 24 hours.
